snippet.title: Amber Heard Keeps 'Aquaman' Role As Johnny Depp Is Fired
snippet.description:
After Warner Bros. fired Johnny Depp from "Fantastic Beasts", but kept Amber Heard in the "Aquaman" franchise, Graeme O'Neil and Keshia Chante discuss during "ET Canada Live".
